   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"It is the scribe Victor who writes to the scribe Taurinos the assistant. Send Doses to me to Ashmounein now. There is this letter for you, for there is need.";Back: "Give it to Apa Taurinos, Master, from Apa Victor."</ab>
         </div>
